snippet.title: Hedgehog Launch 2 Flash Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Hedgehog Launch 2 is the sequel to the original Hedgehog Launch, adding many new upgrades and neat improvements.  This time he wants to make it to The Moon, and then to Mars!  Help our guy go far!
